            <section itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" class="faq_section">
                <div data-toggle-for="613bce99bf423" class="faq_section--head"><h2 itemprop="name"
                                                                                   class="header__subsection">Do you
                        have a mobile app?</h2>
                    <button class="faq_section--toggle faq_toggle" aria-label="Toggle"></button>
                </div>
                <div id="613bce99bf423" class="faq_article_overlay" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer"
                     itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                    <article itemprop="text"><p>Yes, we do.<br>
                            You can download the app for iOS by <a target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                                                                   href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/novavoip-contactq-mobile/id698713196?l=ru&amp;ls=1&amp;mt=8">clicking
                                here</a>.<br>
                            You can download the app for Android by <a target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                                                                       href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.infratel.novavoip">clicking
                                here</a>.</p></article>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" class="faq_section">
                <div data-toggle-for="613bce99bf426" class="faq_section--head"><h2 itemprop="name"
                                                                                   class="header__subsection">Do you
                        support all SIP phones? How to connect SIP?</h2>
                    <button class="faq_section--toggle faq_toggle" aria-label="Toggle"></button>
                </div>
                <div id="613bce99bf426" class="faq_article_overlay" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer"
                     itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                    <article itemprop="text"><p>SIP phone and deskphone support is available on the Standard and
                            Ultimate plans.<br>
                            You can view the instructions on how to setup SIP phones here:<br>
                            <a target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                               href="/support/advanced-settings/set-up-a-third-party-sip-phone/">/support/advanced-settings/set-up-a-third-party-sip-phone/</a>
                        </p></article>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" class="faq_section">
                <div data-toggle-for="613bce99bf427" class="faq_section--head"><h2 itemprop="name"
                                                                                   class="header__subsection">Can I
                        customize the voicemail greeting?</h2>
                    <button class="faq_section--toggle faq_toggle" aria-label="Toggle"></button>
                </div>
                <div id="613bce99bf427" class="faq_article_overlay" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer"
                     itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                    <article itemprop="text"><p>Yes, you can either record your own greeting or download something from
                            your computer.<br>
                            The maximum file size is 10Mb.</p></article>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" class="faq_section">
                <div data-toggle-for="613bce99bf428" class="faq_section--head"><h2 itemprop="name"
                                                                                   class="header__subsection">Do you
                        provide voicemail to text transcription?</h2>
                    <button class="faq_section--toggle faq_toggle" aria-label="Toggle"></button>
                </div>
                <div id="613bce99bf428" class="faq_article_overlay" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer"
                     itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                    <article itemprop="text"><p>Yes, voicemail to text transcription is available on the Standard and
                            Ultimate plans. You can read voicemails in the mobile app or in the webpanel.<br>
                            Voicemail transcriptions are also automatically sent to your email.<br>
                            More information about voicemail transcription is here:<br>
                            <a target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                               href="/features/voicemail-voicemail-to-text/features.blade.ph">/features/voicemail-voicemail-to-text/</a>
                        </p></article>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" class="faq_section">
                <div data-toggle-for="613bce99bf429" class="faq_section--head"><h2 itemprop="name"
                                                                                   class="header__subsection">Can I
                        export my call log history?</h2>
                    <button class="faq_section--toggle faq_toggle" aria-label="Toggle"></button>
                </div>
                <div id="613bce99bf429" class="faq_article_overlay" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer"
                     itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                    <article itemprop="text"><p>Yes, call export is possible in 2 formats: xls and csv.</p></article>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" class="faq_section">
                <div data-toggle-for="613bce99bf42a" class="faq_section--head"><h2 itemprop="name"
                                                                                   class="header__subsection">Is there a
                        limit on the number of calls that I can record?</h2>
                    <button class="faq_section--toggle faq_toggle" aria-label="Toggle"></button>
                </div>
                <div id="613bce99bf42a" class="faq_article_overlay" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer"
                     itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                    <article itemprop="text"><p>No. Our call recording feature is connected to your novavoip Cloud, so
                            you can record all your calls without worrying about storage space. To avoid clutter
                            however, calls recorded within the novavoip system are only stored for 1 year before being
                            automatically removed. To avoid losing any call recordings, you can export your call records
                            at any time. Call recording is included in our Standard and Ultimate plans.</p></article>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" class="faq_section">
                <div data-toggle-for="613bce99bf42b" class="faq_section--head"><h2 itemprop="name"
                                                                                   class="header__subsection">Can I set
                        up business hours using your service?</h2>
                    <button class="faq_section--toggle faq_toggle" aria-label="Toggle"></button>
                </div>
                <div id="613bce99bf42b" class="faq_article_overlay" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer"
                     itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                    <article itemprop="text"><p>Yes, the business hours settings is available in all our plans.<br>
                            More information about business hours settings is here:<br>
                            <a target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                               href="/features/after-hours-call-routing/features.blade.ph">/features/after-hours-call-routing/</a>
                        </p></article>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" class="faq_section">
                <div data-toggle-for="613bce99bf42c" class="faq_section--head"><h2 itemprop="name"
                                                                                   class="header__subsection">Do you
                        provide an option to block callers?</h2>
                    <button class="faq_section--toggle faq_toggle" aria-label="Toggle"></button>
                </div>
                <div id="613bce99bf42c" class="faq_article_overlay" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer"
                     itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                    <article itemprop="text"><p>Yes, the call blocking feature is available in all our plans.<br>
                            You can block callers from both the web panel and from the mobile app.<br>
                            More information about call blocking is here: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                                                                             href="/features/vip-or-blacklist-calls-routing/features.blade.ph">/features/vip-or-blacklist-calls-routing/</a>
                        </p></article>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" class="faq_section">
                <div data-toggle-for="613bce99bf447" class="faq_section--head"><h2 itemprop="name"
                                                                                   class="header__subsection">Do you
                        offer some sort of dashboard to monitor my team performance?</h2>
                    <button class="faq_section--toggle faq_toggle" aria-label="Toggle"></button>
                </div>
                <div id="613bce99bf447" class="faq_article_overlay" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer"
                     itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                    <article itemprop="text"><p>Yes, the dashboard and corresponding statistics are available in all our
                            plans.<br>
                            novavoip shows you the 5 most essential statistics of your business in the Key.<br>
                            Performance Indicators and Volume sections:<br></p>
                        <ul style="margin: 0">
                            <li style="margin: 0">Connected vs. Missed Calls Report</li>
                            <li style="margin: 0">Average Speed of Answer &amp; Average Talk Time Report</li>
                            <li style="margin: 0">Incoming &amp; Outgoing Calls Report</li>
                            <li style="margin: 0">Internal Calls Report</li>
                            <li style="margin: 0">Voicemails report</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p style="margin: 0">More information about the dashboard is here: <a target="_blank"
                                                                                              rel="noopener"
                                                                                              href="/features/performance-reports/features.blade.ph">/features/performance-reports/</a>
                        </p></article>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question" class="faq_section">
                <div data-toggle-for="613bce99bf448" class="faq_section--head"><h2 itemprop="name"
                                                                                   class="header__subsection">How
                        difficult is it to set-up the system?</h2>
                    <button class="faq_section--toggle faq_toggle" aria-label="Toggle"></button>
                </div>
                <div id="613bce99bf448" class="faq_article_overlay" itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer"
                     itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
                    <article itemprop="text"><p>Because novavoip doesn`t require any hardware or technical
                            installation, it honestly is not terribly difficult. There are a lot of options to alter
                            once you log in, but if you have experience using any CRMs or phone systems, choosing how
                            you want it to run shouldn`t take more than 5-10 minutes.</p>
                        <p>If you don`t have any experience with this kind of software, we offer quick <a
                                href="/live-onboarding/">live onboarding</a> to help walk you
                            through setup and maximize the settings for your business needs. If you`re hesitant at all
                            about setup once you look at the system, we suggest opting for live onboarding to make the
                            experience easier.</p></article>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
